          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col items-start px-4 md:px-12">
        <div
          class="mb-6 p-4 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-50 to-orange-50 inline-block"
        >
          <svg
            class="w-10 h-10"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke="url(#emmergia-gradient-2)"
          >
            <defs>
              <linearGradient
                id="emmergia-gradient-2"
                x1="0%"
                y1="0%"
                x2="100%"
                y2="100%"
              >
                <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#db2777"></stop>
                <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#f97316"></stop>
              </linearGradient>
            </defs>
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium text-gray-900 mb-4 leading-snug">
          Tu cuenta est치 totalmente <br class="hidden md:block" /> protegida y segura.
